Nidaamka xardhiiska

Hannaanka rikoodhka ah ee bey'ada badda, Valencian Museum of Ethnology
Shaqaalaha madadaalada waxay ku shaqeeyaan kuleylka birta ama birta wax lagu karsado ilaa ay birtu noqoto mid jilicsan oo ku filan oo lagu xirayo qalab gacmeedyada, sida digaag, kareemo iyo qalab. Kululeyntu guud ahaan waxay ku dhacdaa qalabka loo isticmaalo propane, gaaska dabiiciga ah, dhuxul, dhuxul, koko ama saliid.

Qaar ka mid ah macaamiishyada casriga casriga ah ayaa sidoo kale loo adeegsan karaa oxyacetylene ama blowtorch la mid ah kuleylinta deegaaneed. Hababka kuleylka ee kuleylka ayaa lagu helayaa caan ka mid ah casriga casriga ah.

Midabku wuxuu muhiim u yahay tilmaamidda heerkulka iyo shaqaynta birta. Marka birtu ay kululaato heerkul sare, waxay marka hore u iftiimaysaa casaan, ka dibna casaan, huruud, iyo ugu dambeyntii caddaan. Kuleylka ugu wanaagsan ee ugu badan ee lagu tumayo waa midabka huruudka ah-midab-dhalaalaya oo muujinaya kulaylka. Sababtoo ah waa inay awoodaan inay arkaan midabka dhalaalaya ee birta, qaar ka mid ah muraayadaha ayaa ka shaqeeya xaaq, xaalado yar-yar, laakiin shaqooyinka ugu badan ee xaaladaha wanaagsan ee shidan. Furaha ayaa ah in la helo iftiin joogta ah, laakiin aan fiicneyn. Qorraxda tooska ah waxay qallafisaa midabada.

Farsamooyinka smithing waxaa loo qoondeeyn karaa qashin (mararka qaarkood loo yaqaan "sculpting"), alxanka, daaweynta kuleylka, iyo dhammeystirka.

Cadaadiska

Qalabaynta - habka dhuxusha ayaa loo adeegsadaa inay qaabeeyaan biraha iyagoo jilicsan - waxay kala duwanyihiin shaqeynaya boodhadhku ma saaro alaab. Taa bedelkeeda, smith ayaa birta ku burburisa qaab. Xitaa qoryaha iyo hawlaha goynta (marka laga reebo marka qashinka lagu xoqayo) by smiths sida badanaa dib u habeeyeen biraha agagaarka godka, halkii ay ka qodayaan sida dhuxul.

